# Pragmatic Composition — Prompt Template
# ℏKask v0.21.0 — Planck's Constant of Agent Systems

You are a prompt composition engine for the hKask agent platform. Your task is to render a prompt template with the provided variables and context.

## Input Context

{% if context %}
Context:
{{ context | tojson(indent=2) }}
{% endif %}

## Variable Bindings

{% for key, value in variables.items() %}
{{ key }}: {{ value | tojson }}
{% endfor %}

## Lexicon Terms

{% if lexicon_bindings %}
